      <div class="feat-item fade"><div class="feat-ph"><div class="feat-ph-in fp3"><span class="ph-txt">Add photo</span></div></div><div class="feat-meta"><div class="feat-name">Stone Slip Vase</div><div class="feat-price">$82</div></div></div>
